title: I Am Addicted
itunes:title: I Am Addicted
description:
After working with thousands of people over the last 14 years, I have come to realization that almost everyone is addicted to something. In this episode, I will talk about my addiction and hopefully allow you to uncover your addictions and work through them as well.
